data.description: If you are looking for a home that is light, bright and airy, this is the home! The main level boasts gleaming hardwood floors, master on the main with a large walk in closet. The master bath has a separate tub and shower and the laundry in the half bath. The kitchen has a new gas stove and microwave and comes with an eat in kitchen with a gorgeous bay window. All windows in the home have a lifetime warranty that is transferrable to the new homeowner. Upstairs you will find 2 additional bedrooms each with their own oversized closet. The 4th and final bedroom is also upstairs, but this one is oversized and has a large walk in corner closet with a closet system! There is room for expansion in the basement with a large unfinished bonus room and there is also a half bath in the basement. On the outside you will find the deck overlooks a large fenced back yard, 3/4 acre culdesac lot in a small subdivision with no HOA.
